name: Briscoe
content:
Briscoe was a Human male smuggler fence who operated near the Blood Razors downed transport on the planet Lok during the Galactic Civil War.
Briscoe was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Briscoe was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
